m the delegate, or if it returns ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"standard callout view has no accessory view on its right side. The return value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of this method is ignored if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"text":" is present in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the delegate.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To display a view on the callout’s left side, implement the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:leftCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to modify the view that is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the right side of the standard callout bubble.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"mapView:rightCalloutAccessoryViewForAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:rightcalloutaccessoryviewforannotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the view to display on the right side of the standard callout bubble."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":